{"name": "netbox-floorplan-plugin", "metadata": {"name": "netbox-floorplan-plugin", "version": "0.5.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/netbox-community/netbox-floorplan-plugin.git", "license": "LGPLv3+", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Netbox Plugin to support graphical floorplans", "upload_time": 1733699675}, "documentation": ["# NetBox Floorplan Plugin\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/netboxlabs/netbox-floorplan-plugin/workflows/tests/badge.svg\" alt=\"Tests\"/>\n\nOriginally Forked from https://github.com/tbotnz/netbox_floorplan\n\n## Demo\n![demo](/media/demo.gif)\n\n## Summary\nA netbox plugin providing floorplan mapping capability for locations and sites\n\n- provides graphical ability to draw racks & unracked devices on a floorplan\n- support for metadata such as labels, areas, walls, coloring\n- floorplan object mapped to sites or locations and click through rack/devices\n- keyboard controls supported\n- export to svg\n\n## Compatibility\n\n| NetBox Version | Plugin Version |\n|-------------|-----------|\n| 3.5         | >= 0.3.2  |\n| 3.6         | >= 0.3.2  |\n| 4.0.x       | 0.4.1     |\n| 4.1.x       | 0.5.0     |\n\n## Installing\n\nThe plugin is available as a Python package in pypi and can be installed with pip  \n\n\n```\nsudo pip install netbox-floorplan-plugin\n```\nEnable the plugin in /opt/netbox/netbox/netbox/configuration.py:\n```\nPLUGINS = ['netbox_floorplan']\n```\nEnable Migrations:\n```\ncd /opt/netbox\nsudo ./venv/bin/python3 netbox/manage.py makemigrations netbox_floorplan_plugin\nsudo ./venv/bin/python3 netbox/manage.py migrate\nsudo ./venv/bin/python3 netbox/manage.py collectstatic\n```\n\nRestart NetBox and add `netbox-floorplan-plugin` to your local_requirements.txt\n\nSee [NetBox Documentation](https://docs.netbox.dev/en/stable/plugins/#installing-plugins) for details\n\n## Mentions\n\nForked from https://github.com/tbotnz/netbox_floorplan\n\nSpecial thanks to Ziply Fiber network automation team for helping originally helping to conceive this during the NANOG hackathon\n\n## Release process\n\nUpdate `netbox_floorplan/version.py` with a new version number, create a new Github release with the same number, the pypi publish workflow will run.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.navigation", "documentation": ["Define the plugin menu buttons & the plugin navigation bar enteries."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.navigation.menu_buttons", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "netbox_floorplan.navigation.menu_items", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "netbox_floorplan.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.utils.file_upload", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Return a path for uploading image attchments.\nAdapted from netbox/extras/utils.py"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets.FloorplanFilterSet", "bases": ["NetBoxModelFilterSet"], "methods": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets.FloorplanFilterSet.search", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "queryset", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets.FloorplanFilterSet.Meta", "bases": [], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets.FloorplanFilterSet.Meta.model", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "netbox_floorplan.filtersets.FloorplanFilterSet.Meta.fields", "type": nul